reviewText: E​s un curso bastante completo en cuanto a la materia pero poco dinámico.

I was reporting technical problems on the Medium website as I was unable to open any link to this site, as a result, I missed all articles throughout the course and no one responded to me and the problem remains.
Now I am trying to log into the exercise test but as usual, it's not working and the page is not available.
that's the link to the exercise test - https://medium.com/astec/how-to-build-a-legal-product-61a7fad4f178.
how is it possible to submit my assignment in this situation ???
T​hanks to all the efforts. Well made Course structure and Presentations. I would recommend it to anyone curious about LegalTech.
It was exciting taking this course, it has a very wide scope that covers everything you need to know about Legal Tech in this digital era.
Super blend of technology and Legal; great global view - final assignment was simply great.
A good course describing trends in legal technology around the world especially relating to adjudication of disputes and innovative approaches.
